_sText:
Most flexible achievement map for CS:Source.I was personally looking for a good achievement map to farm kills but couldn't find one. So I decided to make one myself.
All commands are set in the logic_auto of map. No trouble in setting commands!!
>>Just Join and Enjoy.<<

-Achievements You can GET:

-All "Weapon" Achievements and many more if you try. There are so many. Except Defusal and Bomb achievements ofc. You can get more than 6000 Kills in an hour.
